latestPosts.caption:
My mom really never fails to surprise me & make me feel like a literal princess 🥹❤️ not a post for the number but for the journey. 8th grade Shulka would’ve NEVER seen this coming, She was just out here making random content with 0 clue and 100 dreams… and now there’s 100,000 of you watching, supporting, hyping her up?? like WHAT. 100K??? be fr 😭💗 from my first follower being my mom to now having a fam of 100,000 of you. my brain simply cannot compute.Never in my wildest middle school daydreams did I think I’d come this far.From “who’s even gonna watch this” to “omg 100K people just did??”
This journey has been surreal, chaotic, wholesome & full of growth — and I’m beyond grateful for every single one of you who’s been part of it. i read every dm, comment, story reply and all i can say is you guys are truly precious to me. I love each n every one of you from the bottom of my heart 💗
this is OUR journey & we’re just getting started 🫶
This is your sign to keep chasing because dreams do come true🥹💗cheers
